snippet.title: Tiny Thor - Gameplay Teaser (August 2020)
snippet.description:
This is the latest gameplay video of our upcoming indie game Tiny Thor. We hope you like what you see ;-)

Feel free to join our Discord: https://discord.gg/bXHrrwZ

Website: https://asylumsquare.com/games/tiny-thor
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/541310/Tiny_Thor/

Credits:
Code by Jochen Heizmann
Game Design by Steffen Künstler
Art & Animation by Henk Nieborg, Nauris Amatnieks, Andrew Bado & Emmanuel Henné
Music by Chris Hülsbeck & Fabian Del Priore
